          array (
            'file' => '1958lire50.jpg',
            'alt' => '',
          ),
          'question' => 'Is the 50 lire coin of 1958 rare?',
          'answer' => 'The 50 lire coins of 1958 are considered modestly rare and, despite the print run of  825.000 copies, they aren\'t  easily available. There is a numismatic interest for this coin at all degrees of conservation.  The value goes from 20 to 2000 euros for the copies newly minted!',
