          'question' => 'How much is the 5 lire coin of 1956 worth?',
          'answer' => 'The limited print run of the 5 lire of 1956 (only 400.000 copies) makes these issues fairly rare. These small coins have a value of 50 euros even in a not good state of preservation. The value in state of newly minted conservation is instead conspicuous, about 1500 euros!',
